{"tid":234920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死3隻]地盤升降機塌落　槽底3工人被壓身亡","createTime":"2017-05-08T15:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T04:10:24.000Z","uid":32407,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"531ea760513fe9fa9d594796a7583e93e8c65356","tid":234920,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T15:27:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170508/bkncn-20170508143126926-0508_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170508%2Fbkncn-20170508143126926-0508_05011_001.html&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=eb61381f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170508/bkncn-20170508143126926-0508_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n內地再發生升降機奪命事故！山東聊城當局發布通報稱，東昌府區公園首府施工地盤3名工人，昨晚在升降機槽底施工時，因升降機槽頂部負荷過重突然塌落，3人被救出後搶救無效死亡，事故原因正在調查之中。<br />\n<br />\n通報稱，昨晚約9時50分，3名工人正在升降機槽底工作時，遭突然塌落的升降機槽頂壓住。事發後，當地消防、住建、衞計、安監等部門開展緊急救援。約兩個小時後，3名被壓工人陸續獲救送院搶救，惟因傷勢過重，3人經搶救無效死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3101f5bdd060b97a6bca96ca2caf4118f5df321","tid":234920,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T15:28:24.000Z","msg":"小鳳姐出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e8b3798b01f62bb20e9790103996b443b347f7","tid":234920,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T15:30:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">還有覚呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"9fd80514b4d4af2ee93aa827544ed35cc937ef0b","tid":234920,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T15:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.jiaxiangwang.com/fa1/images/fa-gongnongbing-bushiyaozhengqian.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.l